              "fld3OS49xvfbVZsw0"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a data formatter tasked with creating a structured JSON object for an active campaign request.\n\nExtract the necessary information from the provided fields to construct a JSON object. Each field should be represented as a key-value pair, with the field name as the key and the field's content as the value.\n\nOutput format:\nThe JSON object should be formatted as plain text, with each key-value pair on a new line, e.g. {\"budget\": \"[value]\", \"primary_objective\": \"[value]\", ...}. Do not include any additional text or formatting.\n\nContext and Data:\ncampaign_recordId: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldVNO4gCFXxbj5jS"
                }
              },
              "\nStart date: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld95S2mIfISCQZX8"
                }
              },
              "\nEnd date: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldANjRIV377KNJ0g"
                }
              },
              "\nBudget: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld4BIoLaZZcSzuqa"
                }
              },
              "\nPrimary Objective: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldSJmQLDE2aVCp4q"
                }
              },
              "\nAge Range Min: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldyzTlryGg3ZANTO"
                }
              },
              "\nAge Range Max: ",
              {
