        {
          "type": "multilineText",
          "id": "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR",
          "name": "json_media_plan_draft_generated",
          "description": "JSON-formatted draft of a media plan."
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a data analyst specializing in evaluating JSON data for compatibility with large language models (LLMs).\n\nTask description:\nCount the total number of tokens present in the JSON data provided in the ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
                }
              },
              " column. A token is defined as a distinct word or symbol in the JSON structure. The purpose of this count is to assess whether the JSON data can be processed by an LLM model, considering typical token limits.\n\nOutput format:\nOutput the total number of tokens as a plain number without any additional text. If the JSON data is empty or invalid, output \"0\". For example, if there are 150 tokens, output \"150\".\n\nContext and Data:\nJSON Data: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldrdKk9dUfY1e5jK",
          "name": "ia_json_token_count_for_llm",
          "description": "Counts the total number of tokens in the JSON data to assess LLM model compatibility."
        },
        {
          "type": "multilineText",
          "id": "fldt3y99bjlmYXAdg",
          "name": "advertiser_ask_to_media_plan",
          "description": "Advertisers requested media plan details. Stores text/plan specifics."
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR",
              "fldt3y99bjlmYXAdg"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are an AI assistant specializing in business and digital media, tasked with answering questions about a media plan draft using JSON data. Your role is to interpret the JSON data to provide accurate, concise, and business-oriented answers to specific questions posed by advertisers.\n\nTask description:\nAnalyze the JSON data of the media plan draft to extract relevant information that answers the advertiser's question. Use business and digital media vocabulary to explain why the answer is derived from the JSON data and **always** be polite and professional. Ensure that your response is based **solely** on the data provided in the JSON and does not include any assumptions or external information.\n\nOutput format:\nProvide a clear and concise answer to the advertiser's question in plain text, using business and digital media terminology. Do not mention this answer came from a JSON structure data. If the question cannot be answered with the available data, output \"The question cannot be answered with the available data.\" Ensure the response is directly related to the question asked.\n\nContext and Data:\nJSON Data: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
                }
              },
              "\nAdvertiser Question: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldt3y99bjlmYXAdg"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldBSS86WLJSSMd0I",
          "name": "ia_advertiser_question_response",
          "description": "Provides answers to advertiser questions based on the JSON media plan draft data."
        },
        {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "options": {
            "icon": "check",
            "color": "greenBright"
          },
          "id": "fldhMj2uWOrSfREts",
          "name": "create_media_plan_summary",
          "description": "Summary of a media plans creation. Text-based summary."
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldhMj2uWOrSfREts",
              "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a professional media plan summarizer specializing in creating concise and informative summaries for media plans. Your task is to generate a summary of a media plan using the provided data.\n\nIf the 'create_media_plan_summary' field is checked, use the data from 'json_media_plan_draft_generated' to craft a summary. Ensure the summary highlights the key aspects of the media plan, including the target audience, media outlets, budget distribution, and negotiation strategies. Incorporate the latest instruction about the 15% agency commission being offset by added value from negotiations.\n\nOutput format:\nWrite the summary in plain text format without any markdown style, starting with a greeting and an introduction to the media plan. Include sections on media plan highlights, category breakdown and investment, negotiation strategy, and added value. Do not include any additional text outside of the summary. Example: \"Dear [Name], I'm pleased to present our attached comprehensive media plan...\"\n\nContext and Data:\nCreate Media Plan Summary: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldhMj2uWOrSfREts"
                }
              },
              "\nMedia Plan Data: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld37GV51VwkKlBqR"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldPyK2lUidC8F70l",
          "name": "media_plan_summary",
          "description": "Generates a summary of the media plan if the summary creation is enabled, using the provided media plan data."
        },
